@endpoint POST /
@desc Starts running a build with the settings defined in the project. These setting include: how to run a build, where to get the source code, which build environment to use, which build commands to run, and where to store the build output. You can also start a build run by overriding some of the build settings in the project. The overrides only apply for that specific start build request. The settings in the project are unaltered.
